## Failure Modes

| Situation | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| Tests fail | Fix them. Do not proceed with failures. |
| Template not rendering | Check Thymeleaf syntax, fragment names, model attributes |
| HTMX endpoint 404 | Verify controller mapping matches `hx-get` path |
| Context filling | `gc runtime request-restart` |
| Backend service down | Use fallback from `@CircuitBreaker`; test with mocked client |

